FBIS4-8753 "dreeu074_i_94026" FBIS-EEU-94-074 Daily Report 17 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Events in Gorazde -- 17 April Events in Gorazde -- 17 April `Horror, Hell' as Tanks Enter Gorazde LD1704162994 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in Serbo-Croatian 1600 GMT 17 Apr 94 LD1704162994 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Excerpt] It is still not known how long Gorazde will live. Is it a question of minutes or hours. It is certainly not a question of days, as chetnik tank have already entered the town. The chaos has begun; horror and hell are in every place [words indistinct]. Chetniks are shooting at the people with snipers and anti-aircraft weapons. There are many casualties but their number is not known in this chaos. Unarmed people are facing chetnik tanks. NATO planes are agonizing [words indistinct]. The town center of Gorazde has become a real enclosure for children, women, and the elderly waiting for the death they have already seen. [passage omitted]
